<div align="center">

  <h1>🌌 NeonHub</h1>
  <h3>Real-Time Cyberpunk Social Platform • Laravel 13 + Vue 3</h3>

  <p>
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Laravel-13-FF2D20?style=for-the-badge&logo=laravel&logoColor=white" alt="Laravel">
